graph TB
    Client["HTTP Client<br/>curl/MCP Bridge"]
    
    subgraph "Authentication Methods (Priority Order)"
        Auth1["Authorization: Bearer TOKEN<br/>(preferred)"]
        Auth2["X-API-Key: TOKEN<br/>(alternative)"]
        Auth3["?api_key=TOKEN<br/>(query param, discouraged)"]
    end
    
    Middleware["require_api_token()<br/>Decorator on routes"]
    
    Client -->|provides| Auth1
    Client -->|provides| Auth2
    Client -->|provides| Auth3
    
    Auth1 -->|extracted by| Middleware
    Auth2 -->|extracted by| Middleware
    Auth3 -->|extracted by| Middleware
    
    Middleware -->|validates against| ConfigTokens["automem.config<br/>API_TOKEN<br/>ADMIN_TOKEN"]
    
    Middleware -->|"if valid"| Handler["Route Handler<br/>Process request"]
    Middleware -->|"if invalid"| Reject["401 Unauthorized<br/>abort(401)"]
    
    AdminEndpoint["/admin/reembed<br/>/enrichment/reprocess"]
    AdminMiddleware["require_admin_token()<br/>Additional check"]
    
    Handler -->|"if admin route"| AdminEndpoint
    AdminEndpoint -->|requires| AdminMiddleware
    AdminMiddleware -->|validates| ConfigTokens